# Web3Forms: https://web3forms.com — register with the inbox where you want contact form mail.
# Copy this file to .env.local (next to package.json), paste your access key, then fully restart the dev server. Vite reads env only on startup.
#
# Prefer VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY. If you still have the old CRA name, REACT_APP_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY also works.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
